# Public, build-time SEO config (NOT a secret) — committed so `$env/static/public`
# always resolves and every build has a sane default.
#
# Canonical site origin: absolute, no trailing slash. Since the site is fully
# prerendered, this is inlined into the static output at build time (there is no
# live request origin). Override it in the environment for preview/staging/CI
# builds (a real PUBLIC_SITE_URL var takes precedence over this file).
PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://wforacle.avyiel.dev
